719837f-a.title: Manhattan: Fort Washington Aven - 183rd Street
719837f-a.text:
Lane leading to the residence of James Gordon Bennett, Fort
Washington Avenue at 183rd Street.
This charming bit of rural Manhattan is now gone, the site being
occupied by apartment houses.
1904.
Photograph by Brown Brothers.
